# multiple

multiple strings

[![NPM version](https://badge.fury.io/js/confirm-cli.png)](http://badge.fury.io/js/confirm-cli)

---

## Install

```bash
$ npm install multiple --save
```

## Usage

```js
var multiple = require('multiple');
multiple('$', 5);  // '$$$$$'
```
